ATM Problem Code: HS08TEST

-----------SoluTion-----------

x,y = map(float,input().split())   # x = Withdrawing Amount , y = Total Balance In The Account
if x%5 == 0:      #  The cash machine will only accept the transaction if X is a multiple of 5
    if (x+0.5)<=y:           
        y = y-(x + 0.50)  #For each successful withdrawal the bank charges 0.50 $US
        print(y)
    else:
        y > x
        print(y)
else:
    print(y)
